title: President pays tribute to Shaheed-e-Millat Liaquat Ali Khan on his death anniversary
content:
ISLAMABAD, Oct 16 (APP): President Asif Ali Zardari on Thursday paid tribute to Shaheed-e-Millat Liaquat Ali Khan on his death anniversary, lauding his historic services for the development and stability of Pakistan after its creation.
In his message, the president said that Liaquat Ali Khanâ€™s honesty, commitment to national unity, and adherence to democratic principles remained a beacon of guidance for the nation even today.
President Zardari said the nation must continue to draw inspiration from the golden principles and vision of its founding leaders.
He prayed to Allah Almighty to elevate the ranks of Shaheed-e-Millat Liaquat Ali Khan in Jannah.
